FBIS4-20964 "jptdd014__l94024" JPRS-TDD-94-014-L JPRS Narcotics 26 March 1994 LATIN AMERICA COLOMBIA Pepes Leader Denies Sending `Threats' to Escobar's Widow Pepes Leader Denies Sending `Threats' to Escobar's Widow PA2803152894 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 1 in Spanish 1800 GMT 26 Mar 94 PA2803152894 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 1 Spanish BFN ["Last-minute report" from the "NTC News" newscast] [Text] Maria Victoria Henao, Pablo Escobar's widow, has just received a letter signed by Fidel Castano, who is said to be the leader of the Pepes [Persecuted by Pablo Escobar]. Castano says he is not the author of the threats received by the Escobar family in recent days.
